snippet.textDisplay: This has completely ruined one of my favorite compositions. Coke Studio MTV please stop destroying classics. If you could have kept the original melody with an up tempo qawali beat "Drums, Tabla, Bass and electric guitar"and let these masters do their own thing it would have been great. They have done this song a million times and every time they do it live they do a great job. This is the worst rendition of this song I have ever heard. Reminds me of Sayonee covered by Rahat Fateh Ali Khan. Utter disappointment.
